title: Active Enzyme Laundry Stain Remover Spray – Deep Cleaning Formula for Stubborn Stains, Oil & Collar Marks on White Shirts & Garments – Powerful Clothing Cleaner (1)
features: 【Powerful Enzyme Formula】This active enzyme stain remover spray breaks down tough stains into water-soluble particles for effortless removal. Its advanced booster prevents re-depositing, ensuring complete stain elimination from fabrics.
【Instant Stain Removal】Works within seconds! Our fast-acting laundry stain remover dissolves coffee, wine, ink, and food stains instantly—no scrubbing or lingering residue.
【Easy Application】For stubborn stains (collars, cuffs), apply a small amount, gently scrub, and rinse. No pre-soaking needed—ideal for busy lifestyles.
【Fabric-Safe & Versatile】Safe for cotton, linen, synthetics, and delicates. Effectively removes organic stains like juice, tea, and grease while preserving fabric quality.
【Portable & Multi-Scenario Use】Compact design for home, travel, or outdoor adventures. Tackle cooking spills, party mishaps, or camping stains anytime, anywhere.
